            <h2 style="color: #00ffff; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">What is Bioluminescence?</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8;">
                Bioluminescence is the production and emission of light by living organisms through chemical reactions. 
                This mesmerizing phenomenon occurs in various species across the ocean depths, forests, and even caves.
            </p>
        </div>

