            </div>

            <div class="organism-card">
                <div class="organism-icon">ğŸª¼</div>
                <h3>Crystal Jellyfish</h3>
                <p>The discovery of Green Fluorescent Protein (GFP) in these jellyfish revolutionized biological research. They glow with a mesmerizing green light when disturbed, serving as both a defense mechanism and communication tool.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="organism-card">
                <div class="organism-icon">ğŸ¦—</div>
                <h3>Fireflies</h3>
                <p>Perhaps the most famous bioluminescent creatures, fireflies use their light to attract mates. Each species has its own unique flash pattern, creating a natural morse code of romance in summer nights.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="organism-card">
                <div class="organism-icon">ğŸ¦</div>
                <h3>Deep Sea Anglerfish</h3>
